      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 157,
      "message": "Could this be part of the common.certInitializer.volumeMount output? This way we don't have to add custom change for every projects that requires custom cert through certInitializer. We could technically enable customCertImport at one place and every components using certInitializer would get custom certs automatically (components could opt-out in their override/value file)\n\nedit: Maybe we can't unless the keystore is mounted at the same place for every components...",
